OL,3,CTUC leader calls for 'year of
OL,4,Cdelivery' for workers
OL,6,FA union leader has called for 2025 to
OL,7,Fbe a "year of delivery" for workers
OL,8,Fafter 14 years of "Tory chaos".
OL,10,FTUC general secretary Paul Nowak said
OL,11,Fin his new year message that working
OL,12,Fpeople desperately needed "tangible
OL,13,Fchange".
OL,15,FHe said: "Repairing and rebuilding
OL,16,FBritain after 14 years of Tory chaos
OL,17,Fand decline is a massive challenge for
OL,18,Fthe Government, but 2025 has to be a
OL,19,Fyear of delivery.
