OL,6,F"Continuing with the same broken
OL,7,Fstatus quo is not an option.
OL,9,F"As recent elections in the US and
OL,10,Facross the globe have shown, securing
OL,11,Feconomic growth is not enough on its
OL,12,Fown. Families want to feel better off
OL,13,Fand to see material improvements in
OL,14,Ftheir day-to-day lives."
OL,16,FImproving job quality and putting more
OL,17,Fmoney into people's pockets was an
OL,18,F"urgent national mission", said Mr
OL,19,FNowak, adding: "Working households up
OL,20,Fdown this country are hurting and we
OL,21,Fcannot afford to ignore it.
