OL,3,CTUC leader calls for 'year of
OL,4,Cdelivery' for workers
OL,6,F"The Government has a historic
OL,7,Fopportunity ` and an electoral mandate
OL,8,F` to make work pay.
OL,10,F"Delivering the Employment Rights Bill
OL,11,Fin full will boost living standards
OL,12,Ffor millions and create a happier,
OL,13,Fhealthier and more productive
OL,14,Fworkforce.
OL,16,F"We must not get distracted or
OL,17,Fdiverted from this task. Creating
OL,18,Fbetter-quality jobs also requires an
OL,19,Findustrial strategy worthy of its name
OL,20,F` something we never got under the
OL,21,FTories."
