OL,6,FA Government spokesperson said: "Our
OL,7,FPlan to Make Work Pay is a core part
OL,8,Fof the mission to grow the economy,
OL,9,Fraise living standards across the
OL,10,Fcountry and create opportunities for
OL,11,Fall. It will tackle the low pay, poor
OL,12,Fworking conditions and poor job
OL,13,Fsecurity that has been holding our
OL,14,Feconomy back.
OL,16,F"The plan will help more people to
OL,17,Fstay in work, improve job security and
OL,18,Fboost living standards. Once
OL,19,Fimplemented, the plan will represent
OL,20,Fthe biggest upgrade of workers' rights
OL,21,Fin a generation."
